<div class='talk-article__body talk-transcript__body'>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='230' id='t-230'>I can't help but this wish:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1583' id='t-1583'>to think about when you're a little kid,
