<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='8652' id='t-8652'>what would it be?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='10183' id='t-10183'>And I always answered,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='11596' id='t-11596'>&quot;Well, I'd want the wish</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='12930' id='t-12930'>to have the wisdom to know
exactly what to wish for.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='16772' id='t-16772'>Well, then you'd be screwed,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='18147' id='t-18147'>because you'd know what to wish for,
