<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='21186' id='t-21186'>and now, since we only have one wish --
unlike last year they had three wishes --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='25033' id='t-25033'>I'm not going to wish for that.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='26543' id='t-26543'>So let's get to what I would like,
which is world peace.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='31570' id='t-31570'>And I know what you're thinking:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='33626' id='t-33626'>You're thinking, &quot;The poor girl up there,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='35614' id='t-35614'>she thinks she's at a beauty pageant.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='37415' id='t-37415'>She's not. She's at the TED Prize.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='39690' id='t-39690'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='42824' id='t-42824'>But I really do think it makes sense.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='45244' id='t-45244'>And I think that
the first step to world peace</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='47863' id='t-47863'>is for people to meet each other.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='49707' id='t-49707'>I've met a lot of different
