who wanted to take over the world,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='58565' id='t-58565'>to a military press officer in Qatar,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='61000' id='t-61000'>who would rather not take over the world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='63529' id='t-63529'>If you've seen the film
&quot;Control Room&quot; that was sent out,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='66238' id='t-66238'>you'd understand a little bit why.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='67887' id='t-67887'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='69062' id='t-69062'>Thank you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='70244' id='t-70244'>Wow! Some of you watched it.
