</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:24
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='73540' id='t-73540'>So basically what I'd like
to talk about today</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='78134' id='t-78134'>is a way for people to travel,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='81000' id='t-81000'>to meet people in a different way than --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='85000' id='t-85000'>because you can't travel
