<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='99739' id='t-99739'>This is Donna.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='100914' id='t-100914'>This is Donna at the Statue of Liberty.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='104446' id='t-104446'>This is my mother and aunt
