<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='120123' id='t-120123'>it becomes more and more important</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='121790' id='t-121790'>that we learn each other's dance moves,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='123676' id='t-123676'>that we meet each other,
