<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='143860' id='t-143860'>You can't force people, free will.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='145619' id='t-145619'>And I totally support that,
so we're not forcing people to travel.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='148750' id='t-148750'>But I'd like to talk
