<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='159000' id='t-159000'>And that's what I'm going
to talk to you about today.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='163857' id='t-163857'>I was asked that I speak a little bit
about where I personally come from,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='168612' id='t-168612'>and Cameron, I don't know how
