<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='176000' id='t-176000'>because of where I come from.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='178171' id='t-178171'>I'm the daughter of an American mother</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='181574' id='t-181574'>and an Egyptian-Lebanese-Syrian father.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='184709' id='t-184709'>So I'm the living product
