<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='188805' id='t-188805'>No pun intended.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='189981' id='t-189981'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='191012' id='t-191012'>And I've also been called,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='192293' id='t-192293'>as an Egyptian-Lebanese-Syrian American
