<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='218929' id='t-218929'>in Egypt, when I was about 16.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='221326' id='t-221326'>My mother took me there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='223905' id='t-223905'>She's somebody who believes strongly
