<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='241254' id='t-241254'>you can get from sorting through garbage.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='243373' id='t-243373'>And I began teaching there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='244962' id='t-244962'>I taught English, and I met
