<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='258715' id='t-258715'>and just incredible qualities.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='261421' id='t-261421'>I got drawn into this community
and I began to take pictures there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='265199' id='t-265199'>I took pictures of weddings
