<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='278570' id='t-278570'>the UN Conference
on Population and Development</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='283000' id='t-283000'>asked me to show them at the conference.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='285920' id='t-285920'>So I was 18; I was very excited.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='288892' id='t-288892'>It was my first exhibit of photographs
